  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It Is An Open World Insect Life simulator.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/af6145f7003bff7a852e45c7c6fcd368.avif?t=1718554789\" width=512 height=512 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose an insect from those presented in the game. Each insect has its own characteristics. Upgrade the nest, increase the number of the colony. Gather things around the map to expand your nest and colony. Fight other insects and capture their nests. You have the option to recruit companions as a personal squad for easier progression through the game:</h2><li>several Types Of Insects<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/3fa0b377b07a09f994d714535ec48380.avif?t=1718554789\" width=460 height=150 /></span><br></li><li>Several types of nests with the possibility of updating<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/3b03fe427517a58305ad04cc3a4f5d52.avif?t=1718554789\" width=460 height=150 /></span><br></li><li>Increase the number of your colony<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/575418c622a81aeef2bfb2f597385b3c.avif?t=1718554789\" width=460 height=150 /></span> <br></li><li>Recruit part of the colony to your companions<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/5a55e08d11477bb83f592aef9830387a.avif?t=1718554789\" width=460 height=150 /></span> <br></li><li>Сollect surrounding things and use them for upgrades<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/b86d36d50db92db436333113c6643ad3.avif?t=1718554789\" width=460 height=150 /></span></li></ul></h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >It Is An Open World Insect Life simulator.</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/af6145f7003bff7a852e45c7c6fcd368.avif?t=1718554789\" width=512 height=512 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Choose an insect from those presented in the game. Each insect has its own characteristics. Upgrade the nest, increase the number of the colony. Gather things around the map to expand your nest and colony. Fight other insects and capture their nests. You have the option to recruit companions as a personal squad for easier progression through the game:</h2><li>several Types Of Insects<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/3fa0b377b07a09f994d714535ec48380.avif?t=1718554789\" width=460 height=150 /></span><br></li><li>Several types of nests with the possibility of updating<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/3b03fe427517a58305ad04cc3a4f5d52.avif?t=1718554789\" width=460 height=150 /></span><br></li><li>Increase the number of your colony<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/575418c622a81aeef2bfb2f597385b3c.avif?t=1718554789\" width=460 height=150 /></span> <br></li><li>Recruit part of the colony to your companions<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1866090/extras/5a55e08d11477bb83f592aef9830387a.avif?t=1718554789\" width=460 height=150 /></span> <br></li><li>Сollect surrounding things and use them for upgrades<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_i